data.description: Experience elegance and modern comfort in this recently updated Edmonds condo. With its thoughtfully designed kitchen and dining area, you'll find it effortlessly flows into a cozy living space that extends to an inviting outdoor patio. A primary suite, featuring an ensuite and generous closet, pairs harmoniously with two additional bedrooms and a sophisticated hallway bathroom. The community-centric HOA enhances living with a pool, standout amenities, and ample guest parking. Beyond the comforts of home, a brief stroll places you amidst restaurants, coffee shops, and grocery stores. Additionally, the Interurban Trail and Ballinger Park are easily accessible, enriching your living experience.
